<p>Today&#8217;s WordPress MU release is 2.8.4, a <a href="http://ocaoimh.ie/wp-content/plugins/feed-statistics.php?url=aHR0cDovL3dvcmRwcmVzcy5vcmcvZGV2ZWxvcG1lbnQvMjAwOS8wOC8yLTgtNC1zZWN1cml0eS1yZWxlYXNlLw==">security release</a> that fixes an annoying bug that allowed any user to change the admin password. Your password was never at risk however so it&#8217;s more an annoyance than anything else. </p>
