</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</li>
<li><strong>John Lamansky	: <a href="http://weblogtoolscollection.com/pluginblog/2009/07/03/seo-ultimate/">SEO Ultimate</a></strong><br />
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="450">
<col width="450" />
<tbody>
<tr height="17">
<td height="17">This   all-in-one SEO plugin can handle titles, noindex, meta data, canonical tags,   404 error tracking, and more.</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</li>
